{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01CCBeu14ZovCSTTeE5z6jA8","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The pod crdb-cluster-0 is running but waiting for pods 1 and 2 to come up. The PVC for pod 0 is pending - let me check why. The StatefulSet will only bring up pods sequentially (pod 0 first, then 1, then 2 - but only after pod 0 is Ready). Since pod 0 is not ready (it's waiting for peers), the StatefulSet won't start pod 1 and 2.\n\nCockroachDB pods are in a chicken-and-egg situation: pod 0 waits for pods 1 and 2 to form quorum, but pods 1 and 2 won't start until pod 0 is Ready (due to StatefulSet ordered rollout).\nThe solution is to switch the StatefulSet to parallel pod management so all three pods launch at once instead of waiting for each one to be ready first.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3350,"cache_read_input_tokens":30293,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3350},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f97a740c-324d-49d3-94dc-b8172479a1b6","uuid":"79fc4d78-2347-4d74-99b8-0754f69e38bc","request_id":"req_011Cc9XK5Vrn8D2rMKCAbH7P"}
